Liverpool striker, Mohamed Salah today celebrates his golden boot win with a wonderful tweet. Mo Salah who leads Harry Kane of Tottenham Hotspur with 2 goals reaches 32 Premier League goals, setting a new record for a 38-game season! In a tweet to celebrate the award, Salah said: “Golden Boot? come here to daddy”    Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook